# PROJECT OVERVIEW: POLLOSSEUM

## Vision
A cutting-edge political media platform that personalizes content delivery based on users' demographic profiles and ideological preferences.

## Core Features
- Personalized content curation based on:
  - Demographics (nationality, age, location, gender)
  - Ideological alignments (democratic, republican, liberal, feminist, futurist, religious beliefs)
- Real-time trending political issues
- User-specific content recommendations

## Project Philosophy
- Emphasis on high maintainability and scalable architecture
- Senior engineering practices and standards
- Comprehensive documentation

